show.description: A girl lived a quiet life—until a scandal forced her into the spotlight and the arms of powerful CEO. But when secrets about her true identity surface, everything changes. Daughter Of The Secret Tycoon is a tale of hidden legacies, unexpected romance, and a girl who went from overlooked to unstoppable. Watch Now!
